Stixbox Function

NOM

    dchisq - The chisquare density function

SEQUENCE D'APPEL

f = dchisq(x,d)

PARAMETRES

    • x : real
    • d : degree of freedom (x,d can be matrix with common size)
    • f : chisquare density function with d degree of freedom at the values of x

DESCRIPTION

    The chisquare density function
